data.name: rptPOSheet.ReportDefinition
data.value: <!--Report *** Purchase Order Sheet ***--><Report version="2.6.20101.54005"><Name>Purchase Order Sheet</Name><ReportInfo /><DataSource><ConnectionString>Provider=SQLOLEDB;Data Source=thuypt;User ID=sa;Password=;Initial Catalog=MAP;</ConnectionString><RecordSource>SELECT PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.RequiredDate AS 'RequiredDates', PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.Code AS 'PO Number', PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.PORevision AS 'Version', PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.OrderDate, CAST(DAY(PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.RequiredDate) AS VARCHAR) + '/' + CAST(MONTH(PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.RequiredDate) AS VARCHAR) AS RequiredDate, MST_Party.Code AS 'VendorCode', MST_Party.Name AS 'PartyName', MST_Party.Address, MST_PartyContact.Code AS 'ContactCode', MST_PartyContact.Name AS 'ContactName', MST_PartyContact.Phone, MST_PartyContact.Fax, ShipToLoc.Code AS 'ShipLoc', ShipToLoc.Name AS 'ShipLocName', InvoiceLoc.Code AS 'InvLoc', InvoiceLoc.Name AS 'InvLocName', MST_Employee.Code AS 'BuyerCode', MST_Employee.Name AS 'BuyerName', PO_PurchaseType.Code AS 'PO Type', MST_Carrier.Code AS 'Carrier', MST_PaymentTerm.Code AS 'PaymentTerm', MST_DeliveryTerm.Code AS 'DeliveryTerm', PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.Line, ITM_Product.Code AS 'PartNumber', ITM_Product.Description AS 'PartName', ITM_Product.Revision, PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.VendorItem, PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.VendorRevision, PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.OrderQuantity, PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.Adjustment1, PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.Adjustment2, MST_UnitOfMeasure.Code AS 'UM', PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.ProductID FROM PO_PurchaseOrderMaster JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderDetail ON PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.PurchaseOrderMasterID = PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.PurchaseOrderMasterID JOIN ITM_Product ON PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID JOIN MST_MasterLocation AS ShipToLoc ON PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.ShipToLocID = ShipToLoc.MasterLocationID JOIN MST_MasterLocation AS InvoiceLoc ON PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.InvToLocID = InvoiceLoc.MasterLocationID JOIN MST_Party ON PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.PartyID = MST_Party.PartyID JOIN MST_UnitOfMeasure ON PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.BuyingUMID = MST_UnitOfMeasure.UnitOfMeasureID LEFT JOIN MST_PartyContact ON PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.PartyContactID = MST_PartyContact.PartyContactID LEFT JOIN MST_Employee ON PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.BuyerID = MST_Employee.EmployeeID LEFT JOIN PO_PurchaseType ON PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.PurchaseTypeID = PO_PurchaseType.PurchaseTypeID LEFT JOIN MST_Carrier ON PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.CarrierID = MST_Carrier.CarrierID LEFT JOIN MST_DeliveryTerm ON PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.DeliveryTermsID = MST_DeliveryTerm.DeliveryTermID LEFT JOIN MST_PaymentTerm ON PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.PaymentTermsID = MST_PaymentTerm.PaymentTermID</RecordSource></DataSource><Layout><Width>13080</Width><MarginTop>400</MarginTop><MarginRight>500</MarginRight><MarginBottom>400</MarginBottom><Orientation>2</Orientation><PaperSize>9</PaperSize></Layout><Font><Name>Arial</Name><Size>9</Size></Font><Groups><Group><Name>ProductID</Name><GroupBy>ProductID</GroupBy><KeepTogether>1</KeepTogether></Group></Groups><Sections><Section><Name>Detail</Name><Type>0</Type><Visible>0</Visible></Section><Section><Name>Header</Name><Type>1</Type><Height>3780</Height></Section><Section><Name>Footer</Name><Type>2</Type><Height>1485</Height></Section><Section><Name>PageHeader</Name><Type>3</Type><Height>240</Height></Section><Section><Name>PageFooter</Name><Type>4</Type><Height>330</Height></Section><Section><Name>Product</Name><Type>5</Type><Height>1455</Height></Section><Section><Name>ProductID
